author: hwright
msg: When doing wc->wc copies and moves, do all the copies and then, if needed,
the deletes.  The main benefit being that we can reuse the same adm_access
baton for all copy operations.  Copy functionality is not impacted, while
move deletions now occur after all the destinations have been created.
(wc_to_wc_copy_single): Remove.  Move functionality back to wc_to_wc_copy().
(wc_to_wc_copy): Split the main copy loop into two, one which does the
copy, and one which (optionally) does the delete.
